    \ (org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web)\n   - Role: HTTP API server\
    \ framework\n   - Tags: http, api-server\n   - Evidence: Provides embedded web\
    \ server and REST controller support for external API interactions\n\n2. spring-boot-starter-data-jpa\
    \ (org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-data-jpa)\n   - Role: Database\
    \ ORM framework with JPA/Hibernate integration\n   - Tags: database, orm\n   -\
    \ Evidence: Enables database persistence layer for application data storage\n\n\
    3. sqlite-jdbc (org.xerial:sqlite-jdbc:3.46.0.0)\n   - Role: SQLite JDBC driver\n\
    \   - Tags: database, sqlite, jdbc\n   - Evidence: Provides JDBC connectivity\
    \ to SQLite embedded database\n\n4. spring-security-crypto (org.springframework.security:spring-security-crypto)\n\
